snippet.title: ClusterPuck 99 - Nintendo Switch Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Out now on Nintendo Switch!

ClusterPuck 99 is a lightning-paced 8-player sports game created for parties, competition and smack talk!

Bash your friends to gain control of the puck then fight to score, avoiding spikes, ledges and - of course - everyone else.
